    Class and Description
    MalwareIncident
    This class represents the Incident where a malware has been downloaded by the attacker.

    This class represents the Incident that where the attacker attempts to exploit the vulnerabilities emulated in the MSSQL service.

    Network Layer Incident where snort alert is triggered.

    This class represents an Incident on the Application Layer.
